# Serverless URL Shortener

A lightweight, cost-efficient serverless URL shortener built using AWS Lambda, API Gateway, and DynamoDB.

## ðŸ”§ How it Works

- Accepts a POST request with a long URL.
- Generates a 6-character short code.
- Stores the mapping in DynamoDB.
- Returns a shortened URL based on the API Gateway endpoint.

## ðŸš€ Tech Stack

- AWS Lambda (Python)
- Amazon API Gateway
- Amazon DynamoDB

## ðŸ“¬ API Usage

### Endpoint
curl -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d "{\"url\":\"https://example.com/very-long-url\"}" https://chvsmruvq6.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/dev
